{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NetworkMode","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Each mode maps to a specific ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Virtualization.framework"},{"text":" network","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"device attachment type. The mode determines how the guest’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"network traffic is routed relative to the host and the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"external network.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Choosing a Network Mode","anchor":"Choosing-a-Network-Mode"},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Mode","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Guest → Internet","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Host → Guest","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Entitlement","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/NetworkMode\/nat","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"✓","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Via resolved IP"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"None"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/NetworkMode\/bridged(interface:)","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"✓","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Own LAN IP","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"com.apple.vm.networking","type":"codeV